Sheela Sathyanarayana   Jul 28, 2018         [PC3087] Made the component section expand by default.
Haritha Reddy         Sep 04, 2019           [PC-5384] Updated saveCategory method to include logic of adding/removing selected category in List
                                              instead of doing list refresh in controller, for performance improvement.
Kanteti Kishore			Oct 04, 2019		 [PC-5520] created new controller for the component to increase the performance.
